---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Takoyaki Cloud" description="Learn about Project Takoyaki Technologies, LLC and the team behind Takoyaki Cloud.">
  <section class="border-b py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-rose-500">About</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Hosting built for businesses that move fast
      </h1>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground">
        <p>
          Takoyaki Cloud is a product of <strong class="text-foreground">Project Takoyaki Technologies, LLC</strong>. We build cloud infrastructure that's reliable, fast, and simple to use.
        </p>
        <p>
          We started Takoyaki Cloud because we were tired of overpriced VPS providers with confusing pricing, shared IPs, and sluggish networks. Every plan we offer includes dedicated IPv4 and IPv6 addressing and high-speed connectivity &mdash; because that should be the baseline, not the upsell.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our infrastructure is designed for businesses that need dependable hosting without the complexity of hyperscale cloud platforms. Whether you're running a production web app, a staging environment, or a game server, we give you the resources you need and stay out of your way.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-foreground">What we believe</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 h-3.5 w-3.5 shrink-0 text-rose-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-foreground">Transparent pricing.</strong> The price you see is the price you pay.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 h-3.5 w-3.5 shrink-0 text-rose-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-foreground">Performance by default.</strong> 5 Gbps ports and dedicated resources on every plan.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 h-3.5 w-3.5 shrink-0 text-rose-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-foreground">Human support.</strong> When you need help, you talk to a person.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 h-3.5 w-3.5 shrink-0 text-rose-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-foreground">Simplicity.</strong> Hosting shouldn't require a cloud certification.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
